sentences: She has recently been appointed as Director of the ManningCamerata Chamber Players.
She made her solo debut at the age of six with the Omsk Philharmonic Orchestra and the following year was a prizewinner at the Novosibirsk Violin Competition.
In 1990, her family emigrated to Israel where she studied at the Tel Aviv Conservatoire, playing as a soloist with the Tel Aviv Conservatoire Orchestra and the  Young Israel Philharmonic Orchestra.].
